Kochanówka  is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Lidzbark Warmiński, within Lidzbark County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  south of Lidzbark Warmiński and  north of the regional capital Olsztyn.
